Install MySQL Connector

Create database & tables in XAMPP phpMyAdmin

Visit:

http://localhost/phpmyadmin

Create database & tables in XAMPP phpMyAdmin

Visit:

http://localhost/phpmyadmin

Create a table named users:

CREATE TABLE users (
    id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE,
    password VARCHAR(255),
    email VARCHAR(100),
    created_at DATETIME,
    last_login DATETIME
);


Create a table for prediction history:

CREATE TABLE predictions (
    id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(50),
    prediction VARCHAR(50),
    confidence FLOAT,
    timestamp DATETIME
);


How to Make an Admin Account

Option A — Insert using SQL

Run this in phpMyAdmin:

INSERT INTO users (username, email, password, created_at)
VALUES ('admin', 'admin@example.com', 'admin123', NOW());

1. Step 1 — Add column in MySQL

Run this in phpMyAdmin → SQL:

ALTER TABLE users ADD fav_car VARCHAR(100) NULL;


Then in your register page, add an extra field for "Favourite Car".
If you want, I can also modify your register HTML.